{
  "page": "Greyskin",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Greyskin</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Owners</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Haggon\" title=\"Haggon\">Haggon</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Varamyr_Sixskins\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Varamyr Sixskins\">Varamyr Sixskins</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Species</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">Wolf</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Greyskin</b> was the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">wolf</a> that was <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">bonded</a> first to <a href=\"/index.php/Haggon\" title=\"Haggon\">Haggon</a>, and then to <a href=\"/index.php/Varamyr\" title=\"Varamyr\">Varamyr</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greyskin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Haggon and Greyskin had been partners for a long time. When Haggon was near death, he intended for Greyskin to be his \"<a href=\"/index.php/Second_life\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Second life\">second life</a>\". However, the resentful Varamyr, who Haggon had trained, took over control of Greyskin, forcing Haggon from his body, and prevented Haggon from ever having his second life. As Greyskin was old too, he did not long outlive his old master.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greyskin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Prologue\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Prologue\">Prologue</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403204607\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.067 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.263 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node coun